        {
            "_id": "DqaSKvQmVXJGAKRo",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/action.svg",
            "name": "Soul Bolstering",
            "sort": 400000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "passive"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": null
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "deathNote": true,
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>When a suit of wrathful armor is destroyed, it falls to pieces and the soul energy that animated it redistributes to the remaining active suits, trailing prismatic energy and cries of pain as it goes. The first time this occurs, the soul flows into the three remaining suits, granting each suit 4 temporary HP. The second time this occurs, the soul flows into the two remaining suits, granting each 6 temporary HP. The third time this occurs, the soul flows to the one remaining suit, granting it 12 temporary HP. These temporary HP persist until they're lost or until they're replaced by a greater value of temporary HP.</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
                    "license": "OGL",
                    "remaster": false,
                    "title": ""
                },
