                    "value": null
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>A creature that takes damage from a wrathful armor's glaive or gauntlet strike must succeed at a @Check[fortitude|dc:14|traits:disease] save to resist contracting tetanus</p><hr /><p><strong>Tetanus</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Onset</strong> 10 days</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 1</strong> @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Clumsy]{Clumsy 1} (1 week)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 2</strong> @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Clumsy]{Clumsy 2} and can't speak (1 day)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 3</strong> @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Paralyzed] with spasms (1 day)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 4</strong> death</p>"
                },
